# Screenshots Directory

This directory contains screenshot evidence for test cases documented in TESTING_LOG.md.

## Naming Convention

Screenshots should follow this naming pattern:
- `test-[TEST-ID]-[operation-name].png`

## Examples
- `test-cd-001-convert-currency.png`
- `test-fd-001-get-profile.png`
- `test-er-001-invalid-symbol.png`
- `test-pv-001-quote-stock.png`

## Test ID Prefixes
- `cd-` = Core Data Operations
- `fd-` = Fundamentals Operations
- `rd-` = Reference Data Operations
- `er-` = Error Handling Tests
- `pv-` = Parameter Variation Tests

## Notes
- Take screenshots that show both the node configuration and the execution result
- Ensure sensitive data (API keys) are not visible in screenshots
- Use PNG format for best quality



